566
00:38:43,500 --> 00:38:45,000
it's very possible that...

567
00:38:45,000 --> 00:38:49,000
he has the clue about my teacher's case sixteen years ago.

568
00:39:02,500 --> 00:39:05,600
- Search the roof for intruders!
- Roger that!

569
00:39:10,600 --> 00:39:13,400
Your Highness, nobody is outside.

570
00:39:27,600 --> 00:39:30,300
The Book of Mountains and Rivers.

571
00:39:35,800 --> 00:39:38,700
- Who is it?
- It's me.

572
00:39:45,200 --> 00:39:47,000
Come in.

573
00:39:49,500 --> 00:39:52,200
It's so late. What is it?

574
00:39:52,200 --> 00:39:54,000
I saw that you were still awake.

575
00:39:54,000 --> 00:39:56,600
So, I brought a calming incense for you.

576
00:39:57,800 --> 00:40:00,300
Thank you for your care, Your Highness.

577
00:40:05,700 --> 00:40:07,600
Rest well.

578
00:40:31,700 --> 00:40:33,700
Princess, we already have a clue about the book.

579
00:40:33,700 --> 00:40:36,200
What is our next step?

580
00:40:39,400 --> 00:40:41,400
Princess, you can't waver.

581
00:40:41,400 --> 00:40:43,100
You have to be determined.

582
00:40:43,100 --> 00:40:47,200
Please remember that you are Princess Rong Le of Western Qi.

583
00:40:48,400 --> 00:40:50,100
Just focus on hiding yourself well.

584
00:40:50,100 --> 00:40:52,800
Go back the same way when they send out the secret files.

585
