He's just a helpless scholar.

591
00:41:17,800 --> 00:41:19,800
Where can he run?

592
00:41:19,800 --> 00:41:21,400
Li Zhiyuan is very secretive.

593
00:41:21,400 --> 00:41:23,900
We couldn't find him although I had sent out many to do so.

594
00:41:23,900 --> 00:41:26,800
If we can't find him, I'm sure that Prince Li can't find him either.

595
00:41:26,800 --> 00:41:28,600
As long as he stays hidden,

596
